识会被直接拉进黑名单。如果认识好感也会大减。当然吐痰只是举个例子，还有很多类似的事情。也因为这样，我没什么朋友，我总觉得自己好孤独。可是我又不想和那些人去相处。我是不是心里有问题啊。有时候真的搞不懂自己。"},"attached_info":"Cj8InoLJ692Kv7gCEAMaCDc5NjkyNjgxIKOP65IGMAQ4mANAJHIJNTI4MzQ3ODg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"27 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-ba8b5208f900e3f3b1ffa9e3db963b97_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"37_1655426520.5571094","card_id":"Q_537991520","target":{"id":537991520,"title":"如何评价6月16日CSGO针对M4A1的削弱？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/537991520","type":"question","created":1655357774,"answer_count":32,"follower_count":58,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[11591,156106,157750],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"弹夹从25发子弹削弱为20发，备弹80，这会改变其在游戏中的使用率吗？"},"attached_info":"Cj4InoLJ692Kv7gCEAMaCDgxODM1NjIxIM6Cq5UGMAE4OkAlcgk1Mzc5OTE1MjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"27 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-ad5ac2f6ccbcae4bb94af687396c5967_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"38_1655426520.5575962","card_id":"Q_281888002","target":{"id":281888002,"title":"什么食物能大量补充大脑所需营养，让大脑运行更快，每天精力充沛？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/281888002","type":"question","created":1529578017,"answer_count":41,"follower_count":403,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[237,617,5633,19006,28375],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近半年失眠，长期吃垃圾食品，每天疲惫不堪。突发奇想，大量补充大脑所特需营养，是不是能拥有更快速的记忆、逻辑以及精神活力？"},"attached_info":"Cj8InoLJ692Kv7gCEAMaCDI0OTE4MTMzIKGErtkFMAA4kwNAJnIJMjgxODg4MDAyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"27 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer"